          <a href="https://www.yourgenome.org/facts/what-are-infectious-diseases/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
            <div class="news-card news-card-with-image">
              <div class="news-image">
                <span class="news-image keep news-icon-span news-icon-yourgenome" ></span>
              </div>
              <div class="news-story">
                <h4>What are infectious diseases?</h4>
                <p>Infectious diseases are caused by microorganisms such as viruses, bacteria, fungi or parasites and can spread between individuals.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
      </div>
